#: ../../user_manual/indi-setup.rst:4
msgid "INDI Setup"
msgstr "Configuració INDI"

#: ../../user_manual/indi-setup.rst:6
#| msgid ""
#| "&kstars; can control local and remote devices seamlessly via the <link "
#| "linkend=\"what-is-indi\">INDI</link> server/client architecture. INDI "
#| "devices may be run in three different modes:"
msgid ""
"KStars can control local and remote devices seamlessly via the :ref:`INDI "
"<indi-faq-what-is-indi>` server/client architecture. INDI devices may be run "
"in three different modes:"
msgstr ""
"El KStars pot controlar dispositius locals i remots de forma independent "
"mitjançant l'arquitectura servidor/client :ref:`INDI "
"<indi-faq-what-is-indi>`. Els dispositius INDI poden funcionar en tres modes "
"diferents:"

# skip-rule: t-acc_obe
#: ../../user_manual/indi-setup.rst:11
#| msgid ""
#| "<guilabel>Local</guilabel>: The local mode is the most common and is used "
#| "to control local device (&ie; a device attached to your machine)."
msgid ""
"``Local``: The local mode is the most common and is used to control local "
"device (i.e. a device attached to your machine)."
msgstr ""
"``Local``: El mode local és el més comú i s'utilitza per a controlar "
"dispositius locals (és a dir, un dispositiu connectat a la vostra màquina)."

# skip-rule: t-acc_obe
#: ../../user_manual/indi-setup.rst:15
#| msgid ""
#| "<guilabel>Server</guilabel>: The server mode establishes an INDI server "
#| "for a particular device and waits for connections from remote clients. "
#| "You cannot operate server devices, you can only start and shut them down."
msgid ""
"``Server``: The server mode establishes an INDI server for a particular "
"device and waits for connections from remote clients. You cannot operate "
"server devices, you can only start and shut them down."
msgstr ""
"``Servidor``: El mode servidor estableix un servidor INDI per a un "
"dispositiu en particular i espera connexions provinents de clients remots. "
"No és possible operar dispositius de servidor, tan sols podreu pujar i "
"baixar el servei."

# skip-rule: t-acc_obe
#: ../../user_manual/indi-setup.rst:20
#| msgid ""
#| "<guilabel>Client</guilabel>: The client mode is used to connect to remote "
#| "INDI servers running INDI devices. You can control remote devices "
#| "seamlessly like local devices."
msgid ""
"``Client``: The client mode is used to connect to remote INDI servers "
"running INDI devices. You can control remote devices seamlessly like local "
"devices."
msgstr ""
"``Client``: El mode client s'utilitza per a connectar a servidors INDI "
"remots que estan executant dispositius INDI. Es poden controlar de manera "
"fluida els dispositius remots com si es tractés de dispositius locals."

# skip-rule: t-acc_obe
#: ../../user_manual/indi-setup.rst:24
#| msgid ""
#| "You can run local device, establish INDI servers, and connect to remote "
#| "clients from the <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu> "
#| "<guisubmenu>Devices</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Device Manager...</"
#| "guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgid ""
"You can run local device, establish INDI servers, and connect to remote "
"clients from the ``Tools`` → ``Devices`` → ``Device Manager...`` menu item."
msgstr ""
"Podeu executar un dispositiu local, establir servidors INDI i connectar amb "
"clients remots des de l'element de menú ``Eines`` → ``Dispositius`` → "
"``Gestor de dispositius...``."

# skip-rule: t-acc_obe
#: ../../user_manual/indi-setup.rst:28
#| msgid ""
#| "Here is a screenshot of the <guilabel>Device Manager</guilabel> window:"
msgid "Here is a screenshot of the ``Device Manager`` window:"
msgstr ""
"Aquí hi ha una captura de pantalla de la finestra del ``Gestor de "
"dispositius``:"

